data.description: Introducing 15126 Hogshead Way, an exceptional end unit townhome in the sought-after Beechtree neighborhood. This well-maintained residence, constructed in 2018, offers a blend of style and functionality with 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a two-car garage and custom blinds throughout.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open and spacious living area, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen spaces. This open floor plan creates an inviting environment, perfect for both entertaining and everyday comfort. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and has easy access to the large deck with a pergola. The walk-out lower level is a standout feature, complete with a full bathroom, making it versatile for various uses, whether it's a recreation area, guest suite, or a home office.   The primary bedroom is your private retreat, featuring an ensuite bathroom with soaking tub and shower with dual showerheads and a walk-in closet. This offers a luxurious and comfortable space to unwind. The property also includes a large fenced-in yard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. The Beechtree Homeowners Association provides access to an array of amenities, including a public golf course, clubhouse, swimming pool, and scenic walking trails, enhancing your overall quality of life.  Schedule a viewing today and seize the chance to call this remarkable townhome your own.
